 focused, but industry focused (i.e. VDI, IOT/ Edge, Blockchain, AI/ Big Data, DevOps) \u2022 Master of Account/ Territory Ownership, True E2E deal management, sound pipeline/ forecasting management skills This role will be based out of our Morrisville, NC headquarters, and report into the NA Data Center business. #### Position Requirements: Minimum Requirements: \u2022 BS or BA degree; or equivalent experience \u2022 3+ years previous sales team leadership and/or management required \u2022 3+ years of Server Sales knowledge is required \u2022 Must have worked in a quota-carrying sales environment; 5+ years Preferred Requirements: \u2022 Previous field (outside) sales experience and inside sales experience preferred \u2022 Experience with hiring and working with talent acquisition to identify top talent \u2022 Excellent communication, collaboration skills, and ability to influence others. \u2022 Demonstrated experience in showing quarter over quarter growth in sales revenue with large accounts \u2022 Face-to-Face customer engagement experience \u2022 Ability to travel throughout NA in the field with inside sellers as needed We are an Equal Opportunity Employer and do not discriminate against any employee or applicant for employment because of race, color, sex, age, religion, sexual orientation, gender identity, status as a veteran, and basis of disability or any federal, state, or local protected class. "
